The idea that the government

18:40.900 --> 18:44.000
had purposely let the
Russian submarines go?

18:44.070 --> 18:45.880
They did purposely let them go.

18:45.930 --> 18:48.800
We were out on the archipelago.

18:48.930 --> 18:50.920
Are you saying the prime minister

18:50.970 --> 18:53.020
ordered you not to mine the submarines?

18:53.070 --> 18:54.980
Yes, that's common knowledge.

18:55.030 --> 18:58.170
Swedish neutrality is a joke.

18:58.230 --> 19:00.670
It always has been.

19:02.570 --> 19:05.570
Did you ever have any reason to believe...

19:13.400 --> 19:15.400
A spy? A traitor?

19:49.370 --> 19:51.170
Okay, thanks.

19:52.300 --> 19:54.130
Sorry, sorry.

19:58.580 --> 19:59.580
You okay?

19:59.630 --> 20:00.620
Yeah.

20:00.670 --> 20:02.140
Come on.

20:04.800 --> 20:06.220
As I said, it was a long day.

20:06.270 --> 20:10.930
I have a pain in the small
of my back when I...

20:11.000 --> 20:13.650
It was uncomfortable to sit there,

20:13.700 --> 20:16.280
so I took it out and put it on the seat.

20:16.330 --> 20:19.630
It was a stupid thing to do.

20:20.870 --> 20:23.070
Shirt, got my shirt.

20:25.930 --> 20:27.400
Shirt...

20:38.500 --> 20:40.570
I've got my shirt.

20:42.870 --> 20:46.900
I've got the shirt, got the shirt.

20:46.970 --> 20:48.840
Got the shirt.

21:11.050 --> 21:12.050
How'd it go?

21:12.100 --> 21:13.970
You all right?

21:14.630 --> 21:15.720
Yeah, yeah.

21:15.770 --> 21:17.550
I'm just, uh...

21:17.600 --> 21:19.730
You okay?

21:24.270 --> 21:26.940
Look, if you need to talk...

21:28.800 --> 21:30.700
No, thanks.

21:33.530 --> 21:34.650
Just, uh...

21:34.700 --> 21:36.970
You have to let it...

21:38.600 --> 21:40.480
Thanks, though.

21:40.530 --> 21:42.150
I'll see you later, yeah?

21:42.200 --> 21:43.870
Yeah, sure.

